{"tid":1766010,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【克警知心友】鍾鎮濤題字盲撐忠誠勇毅 黃秋生怒轟打婆婆：畜牲","createTime":"2019-12-02T09:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T08:02:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bced6267cf5be59d45e5dde71ca1f6b131b0821e","tid":1766010,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:25:09.000Z","msg":"反修例運動抗爭近半年，克警無休止地被轟濫暴濫權，昨日逾38萬人到尖沙嘴參加「毋忘初心大遊行」，防暴警竟向和平參與者發射催淚彈驅散，甚至粗暴推跌跪地婆婆，全民怒轟克警滅絕人性；不過，曾經出席撐警集會的鍾鎮濤，卻不忘自己的「初心」繼續盲撐，甚至親自題字「致香港警察 忠誠勇毅 心繫社會」貼微博，讚揚他的知心友。<br />\n獲《人民日報》表揚為愛國藝人的鍾鎮濤，昨晚將撐警書法貼微博，獲得同聲同氣的大陸網民一致讚好，有網民更上載撐警嫂的書法附和：「偉大警嫂，持家重教。致香港警嫂」鍾鎮濤回覆：「警嫂非常不容易，致敬」有網民留言：「不愧是我欣賞多年的演員，好久沒看到鍾哥拍戲了，多多出來跟我們見面啦！」鍾鎮濤就回覆：「已經拍了，應該很快會看到。」<br />\n鍾鎮濤在微博世界如魚得水，相反，影帝黃秋生就棄微博，轉玩跟世界接軌的Twitter，昨晚秋生在Twitter貼婆婆被克警推跌報道，留言狂轟：「呢啲邦唔係人嚟，畜牲！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191202/large/1575263011_f4d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191202%2Flarge%2F1575263011_f4d2.jpg&h=d64214dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191202/large/1575263011_c4af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191202%2Flarge%2F1575263011_c4af.jpg&h=3cee00ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191202/large/1575263013_452c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191202%2Flarge%2F1575263013_452c.jpg&h=e1ca65e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191202/large/1575263170_6d3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191202%2Flarge%2F1575263170_6d3b.jpg&h=c852d912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191202/60332822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191202%2F60332822&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=f99c58fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191202%2F60332822&h=733a0711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191202/60332822</a>"},{"pid":"07a02e52e5d135e99b770123619490fa817579ce","tid":1766010,"uid":96169,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />書法都簡體<br />\n洗咪去到咁盡"},{"pid":"781c94848921ea5e92c4443285da0eb16d8a69e2","tid":1766010,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07a02e52e5d135e99b770123619490fa817579ce","tid":1766010,"uid":96169,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />書法都簡體<br />\n洗咪去到咁盡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:36:55.000Z","msg":"太繚<br />\n佢個名有無簡體到"},{"pid":"1e6eb73e51bc23f3c089f203e985ef29d3bf766c","tid":1766010,"uid":4857,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"沒有樓就沒有磚其實係咩LOGIC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e273ff147da6eb047b531a0b557bb2b978f4cf","tid":1766010,"uid":22310,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"屌 第二幅P圖嚟<br />\n俾啲誠意好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a356cdc607ff42e37767db68e11bfedb7d249be","tid":1766010,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T09:4